The utils module
================
	
Utilities to help use and understand PyMeta

	>>> import utils

It generates some source I'd like to see

	>>> import path
	>>> expected_directory = path.path( utils.__file__ ).parent / 'generated'
	>>> generated_file = expected_directory / 'fred.py'
	>>> try: generated_file.remove()
	... except: pass

	>>> generated_file.isfile()
	False
	>>> utils.save_source('x = 0','fred')
	>>> generated_file.isfile()
	True

	>>> print file(generated_file).read()
	x = 0
